quran[35]{c,v,t}:
  70,1,"Isteqsa yiwen, af uâaqeb iuran"
  70,2,i ijehliyen. Ur t ipxaûam yiwen
  70,3,"S$uô Öebbi, Bab n tseddaôin"
  70,4,"Lmalayek akked ôôuê, ppalin $uôeS, deg wass idumen smuset igima iseggwasen"
  70,5,"Ihi, eûbeô ûûebô ifazen"
  70,6,"Nitni, s tidep, walan t ibâad"
  70,7,Nwala t d aqôib
  70,8,"Asmi ara yili igenni, am uzzal ifsin"
  70,9,idurar ad ilin am tavuî
  70,10,Aêbib ur isteqsay aêbib
  70,11,"u mwalan. Ad ib$u ube$wvi, assen, ad isebbel tarwa s iwakken, seg uâaqeb, ad ipwafdu"
  70,12,"akked tmeîîut is, akked gma s"
  70,13,akked walag is it iûûôen
  70,14,akked wayen illan di tmurt meôôa; iwakken a t sellken
  70,15,"Xaîi, atan ujajiê"
  70,16,Isexxev agwlim
  70,17,"Issawel i win ixedâan, iaâûa"
  70,18,"ippadamen, ipsemmiden"
  70,19,"Amdan, s tidep, ipwaxleq d aêemmaq"
  70,20,"Ma innul it cceôô, atan di leqlala"
  70,21,"Ma innul it lxiô, ad isquceê"
  70,22,Kkes ed iméulla
  70,23,imezgiyen di téilla nnsen
  70,24,"i ippaken seg ayla nnsen, lêeqq ipwassnen"
  70,25,"i umappar, akked ume$bun"
  70,26,wid ipputebbten s wass iqeîîiyen
  70,27,wid iugaden aâaqeb n Mass nnsen
  70,28,"War ccekk, aâaqeb n Mass nnsen ur illi segs usellek"
  70,29,Wid iêurben af tuzzuft nnsen
  70,30,"kkes ed ar tilawin nnsen, ne$ piklatin nnsen; akka, ur ppulummun"
  70,31,"Wid ib$an sennig waya, widak d tilas ay zegren"
  70,32,"Wid ippaîîafen deg wawal nnsen, di tgallit nnsen"
  70,33,wid ippaîîafen di ccada nnsen
  70,34,wid ipêaraben $ef téilla nnsen
  70,35,"Widak, di leonanat, d imaâzuzen"